Over the past few years , Copenhagen , Denmark and indeed , pretty much everything Scandinavian -LRB- apart from perhaps their 22 million intensively farmed pigs -RRB- , has become super cool .

They boast Noma and Geranium -- two of the best -LRB- and most expensive -RRB- restaurants in the world , amazing social welfare -LRB- thanks to astronomical taxes -RRB- , endless happiness -LRB- Danes routinely come out top on global happiness surveys -- although worryingly , they 're also in second place for the number of anti-depressants consumed per capita -RRB- , fabulously stylish design , Lego and , more recently , the slew of TV drama series that have taken us all by storm .

Even their royal family is cool . Queen
